  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为智慧水产养殖平台设计一个完整的数据架构。核心是多租户系统，每个养殖场独立运营。我先从租户层开始， tenants 表作为整个系统的根节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tenants"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，tenants 作为顶层隔离单元。那权限这块怎么设计？需要支持不同角色管理不同功能模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tenants"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "IAM 模块拆成三层：users 直接关联 tenants，roles 也归属租户，然后 permissions 挂到 roles 下面。这样租户内的用户-角色-权限完全隔离。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "users",
        "roles",
        "permissions",
        "tenants"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我画出 IAM 子图，包含 users、roles、permissions 三个节点，并建立关系链：roles 指向 permissions，表示角色拥有权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "users",
        "roles",
        "permissions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，users 和 roles 的关系要确认一下——是多对多还是一对多？实际业务中一个用户可能有多个角色，比如技术员兼质检员。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "users",
        "roles"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目前我先用 tenants 指向 users 和 roles 表示归属关系。users 和 roles 的具体关联可以隐式表达，或者后续补充中间表。先保持架构图简洁？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tenants",
        "users",
        "roles"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，先这样。接下来是核心业务——养殖管理。ponds 池塘表直接属于租户，然后 production_cycles 生产周期挂到池塘下面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tenants",
        "ponds",
        "production_cycles"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加 Farm 子图，放入 ponds 和 production_cycles，并建立 ponds 到 production_cycles 的关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ponds",
        "production_cycles"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "每个生产周期需要记录 fish_batch_measurements，比如投苗密度、成活率、均重这些批次测量数据。这个要挂到 production_cycles 下面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "production_cycles",
        "fish_batch_measurements"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加 fish_batch_measurements 节点，建立 production_cycles 到它的指向关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "fish_batch_measurements",
        "production_cycles"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "饲料管理 feeds 是租户级别的，不同租户有自己的饲料配方库。库存变动 inventory_transactions 也是租户维度，但会和生产周期有业务关联。",
